                    </div>
                  </div>
                `;
              }).join("")}
            </div>
            <div style="border-left:4px solid #690B1B;background:#FFF8F8;padding:14px 18px;font-size:11px;color:#690B1B;line-height:1.65;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0">
              <strong>Study Strategy Tip:</strong> ${(VARK_TIPS[sc.topVark] || [])[0] || "Review model structures and visual mappings."}
